# 🏗️ Construction Hub — End-to-End Construction Management App

> Minor Project | B.Tech CSE (Computer Networking) | SRM Institute of Science and Technology | May 2025

## 📌 Overview
Construction Hub is a unified digital platform designed to eliminate inefficiencies in the construction sector. It integrates every stage of the building process — from initial planning to final handover — into a single, intuitive application.

## 🚀 Key Features
- 📅 Project Scheduling & Planning
- 👷 Labour Allocation & Management
- 📦 Procurement & Resource Tracking
- 📄 Document Control & Version Management
- 🔧 Equipment Rental Management
- 💬 Stakeholder Communication
- ☁️ Cloud-based Mobile Access
- 📊 Analytics & Reporting

